{
  "stem": "4284.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Of course, I knelt down to assist it, which we were told before and we had before, when I hear whistles and all kinds of commotion because I'm not there and neither is the horse for the head count, for the appell.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I looked over the-- this bulge in the field.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all I could see, Germans with guns drawn, German Shepherds, again, searching for me and the horse.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now I-- I thought because they don't ask questions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, shoot first and then ask later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was no explanation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One person-- no names or such thing didn't exist, no numbers, just one missing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they went out on the field because there was not much of a chance to be anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was a fairly confined area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I found, happily, a stick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I raised my cap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And sure enough, you know, shots rang out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "If my head had been in there, that would be no interview today.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I yelled in German, this horse is giving birth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, I'm here, I'm here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You know, I am doing what I'm supposed to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Well, the first thing that was strange is Germans did not expect to hear German language.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There were not many German-speaking prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so they weren't sure whether or not it's an officer, another soldier, or what.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But when they came over this bluff, if you want to call it that, you know, they raised the gun, and because here I was in my striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But I was able to explain it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they saw the foal half out of its mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So that kind of saved my life.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
